This mod is a rewrite/better version/sequel of Sprint Sprint Sprint (the discontinued mod)

[b][size=5]Features[/size][/b]
[list][*] Allows the player to sprint (Hold to Sprint/Toggle to Sprint option)
[*] Stamina drain option for when you are sprinting
[*] Prevent player from sprinting when stamina is low
[*] All features [url=https://github.com/JessebotX/StardewValleyMods/blob/master/Sprint%20Sprint/docs/configuration.md]highly configurable[/url]
[/list]
[b][size=5]Usage[/size][/b]
When in game (when your farmer can move), use the configured button (default Left Shift) to sprint

[b][size=5]Install[/size][/b]
[u]Dependencies[/u]
[list][*][url=https://smapi.io/]SMAPI[/url] [b](REQUIRED)[/b] - The Stardew Valley mod loader
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/5098]Generic Mod Config Menu[/url] [b](OPTIONALl)[/b] - Allows configuring the options of this mod in game
[/list]
[u]Installation[/u]
[list][*]Install [url=https://smapi.io/]SMAPI[/url]
[*][b](OPTIONALl)[/b] Install [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/5098]Generic Mod Config Menu[/url]
[*]Install this mod and extract/unzip into your Stardew Valley/Mods folder
[/list]need help/don't understand? check out the [url=https://stardewvalleywiki.com/Modding:Player_Guide/Getting_Started]Player's Guide to Installing and Using Mods[/url] and the Stardew Valley Discord

