[b][size=5]Configuration[/size][/b]
See [url=https://github.com/JessebotX/StardewValleyMods/blob/master/Sprint%20Sprint/docs/configuration.md]configuration documentation[/url] for all options There are 2 ways to edit the config file
[list][*]Download optional dependency Generic Mod Config Menu and you can configure the mod to your liking while in the title screen on a much friendlier user interface (A button is added to the title screen in the bottom left to access the config menus.)
[*]Run the game with this mod installed once to generate a config.json in your Stardew Valley/Mods/Sprint Sprint/ folder and directly edit the config.json file with a text editor (i.e. Notepad, Notepad++, Sublime Text, etc.)

If you choose the second option, you NEED to run the game once in order for a config.json to appear.
If the config.json gets replaced/deleted, the game will generate a new config.json with default settings 

